Package project4

Class Provider

  • java.lang.Object
    • project4.Provider

  • public class Provider
extends java.lang.Object
    The Provider class implements the abstract base class User. It contains the setters and getters for its various fields, including the member's name, address, state, city, zipcode, status, and number, all of which are strings. It also implements 3 constructors, based on which arguments are passed, a print method, and methods to access the Provider Directory and find the index of healthcare service codes.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Alan Manning
